---
// Purpose-Built Capabilities section for Energy industry page
---

<section id="capabilities" class="cre-capabilities-section">
  <div class="cre-capabilities-container">
    <span class="section-label">PURPOSE-BUILT CAPABILITIES</span>
    <h2 class="cre-capabilities-headline">
      Energy systems engineered for your workflow
    </h2>

    <div class="cre-capabilities-grid">
      <!-- Asset Monitoring & Predictive Maintenance -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-1.webp" alt="Asset Monitoring & Predictive Maintenance" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Asset Monitoring & Predictive Maintenance</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Unified asset monitoring that aggregates data from SCADA, sensors, and maintenance systems into a single operational view. Predictive algorithms surface maintenance needs before failures occur, preventing unplanned downtime.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Real-time asset health monitoring</li>
            <li>Sensor data aggregation and analysis</li>
            <li>Predictive failure algorithms</li>
            <li>Maintenance scheduling optimization</li>
            <li>Downtime prevention alerts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Operational Performance Tracking -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-5.webp" alt="Operational Performance Tracking" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Operational Performance Tracking</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Real-time dashboards that track asset utilization, efficiency metrics, dispatch performance, and revenue generation. Identify optimization opportunities and make real-time operational decisions with complete visibility.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Utilization and efficiency tracking</li>
            <li>Performance benchmarking</li>
            <li>Dispatch analytics</li>
            <li>Revenue attribution by asset</li>
            <li>Real-time alerts on performance variances</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Maintenance & Workforce Management -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-6.webp" alt="Maintenance & Workforce Management" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Maintenance & Workforce Management</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Integrated maintenance management that optimizes crew scheduling, tracks work orders, manages parts inventory, and ensures technicians have the right resources for every job.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Preventive maintenance scheduling</li>
            <li>Work order management and tracking</li>
            <li>Parts and inventory management</li>
            <li>Crew scheduling and routing</li>
            <li>Maintenance cost analytics</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Regulatory Compliance & Reporting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-2.webp" alt="Regulatory Compliance & Reporting" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Regulatory Compliance & Reporting</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated compliance tracking and reporting that monitors regulatory requirements, captures compliance evidence, and generates audit-ready reports without manual work.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Regulatory requirement tracking</li>
            <li>Automated compliance documentation</li>
            <li>Audit trail capture and management</li>
            <li>Regulatory report generation</li>
            <li>Compliance metrics dashboard</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Energy Trading & Optimization -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-3.webp" alt="Energy Trading & Optimization" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Energy Trading & Optimization</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Market optimization tools that analyze demand forecasts, asset availability, and price signals to automatically identify profitable trading opportunities and optimize dispatch for revenue maximization.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Demand forecasting integration</li>
            <li>Market price integration</li>
            <li>Optimal dispatch recommendations</li>
            <li>Revenue tracking by market</li>
            <li>Trading opportunity identification</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Workforce & Asset Planning -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-7.webp" alt="Workforce & Asset Planning" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Workforce & Asset Planning</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Strategic planning tools that forecast asset retirement timelines, capacity needs, and workforce requirements. Enables proactive capital planning and prevents surprises.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Asset lifecycle tracking</li>
            <li>Capacity forecasting</li>
            <li>Workforce skill gap analysis</li>
            <li>Capital planning optimization</li>
            <li>Scenario planning and modeling</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-capabilities-section {
    background: #0052CC;
    color: #ffffff;
    width: 100vw;
    margin: 0;
    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
    padding: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capability-card {
    background: transparent;
    border: 3px solid #ffffff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .cre-capability-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .cre-capability-description {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-section {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .cre-includes-section strong {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cre-includes-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 4px 0 4px 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li::before {
    content: "â€¢";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-capabilities-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cre-capability-card {
      padding: 28px 20px;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .cre-capability-title {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .cre-capability-description {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cre-includes-list li {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>


